performance_test <- function (predictions) {
  real = c(test$Brownlow.Votes)
  length(predictions)
  length(real)
  n = length(real)
  print(paste("MAE:", sum(abs(predictions - real))/n))
  print(paste("MSE:", sum((real - predictions)^2)))
  print(paste("RMSE:", sqrt(mse/n)))
}
